Units Sold

Region

Dealer

Variant

Engine Specs

Customer Segment

Date

4ï¸âƒ£ Features
Dashboard Capabilities

Vehicle Performance Insights
KPIs, engine specs, monthly trends, horsepower averages.

Revenue & Sales Breakdown
YOY/MOM charts, revenue KPIs, and model profitability.

Customer Segmentation
Donut charts to visualize preferences by segment.

Dynamic Filters
Users can filter by region, dealer, variant, date, customer segment.

Drill-Through Functions
Navigate to dealer-level or variant-level performance pages.

Custom Navigation Panel
Bookmark-based navigation with an intuitive left-side menu.

Year-Month Analysis (Time Intelligence)
YTD, QTD, MTD performance calculations.

Variant Comparison
Compare EcoBoost, GT, Mach 1, and others using bar/line charts.

