ğŸ”Ÿ Key Insights & Business Impact

Top Regions: Identify high-performing markets boosting Mustang GT sales.

Best-Selling Variants: GT Premium and Mach 1 show highest profitability.

Customer Demographics: Premium customers contribute majority revenue.

Dealer-Level Insights: Specific dealers outperform due to regional demand alignment.

Time Trends: Seasonal spikes around Q3 and Q4 driven by promotional events.

1ï¸âƒ£1ï¸âƒ£ Installation & Setup
Requirements

